 が観測されていれば，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
y_{2} & =a_{0}+a_{1}y_{1}+a_{2}y_{0}+\varepsilon_{2}\\
y_{3} & =a_{0}+a_{1}y_{2}+a_{2}y_{1}+\varepsilon_{3}\\
