\end{align*}

\end_inset

を順に計算できる。もちろん，
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{t}$
\end_inset

 は 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{E}_{t-1}\left[\varepsilon_{t}\right]=0$
\end_inset

 （
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{E}\left[\varepsilon_{t}\right]=0$
\end_inset

